sentences.content: Scene narrative progressions let the user describe complex scenes by decomposing it into simpler subscenes.
Going out for pizza
The family is going out for pizza.
The grandparents are both wearing eyeglasses.
The grandfather is wearing a blue shirt.
The grandmother is wearing a purple blouse with a lavender sweater.
The two grandsons are wearing shirts with striped sleves.
Sitting down at table
The family is seated around a table.
The table has a red and white tablecoth.
Four place setting are stacked on the table.
Serving them their order
Their server is named Angela.
She is a young woman with brown hair.
She is wearing a striped blouse, marroon tunic and matching slacks.
She serves pizzas ordered earlier.
Fulfilling their order
The grandkids are having pepperoni pizza.
The grandparents are having sausuage, mushroom and tomato pizza.
The are all drinking ice cold soda with their meal.
